list.query: Letzte Stunde : TRUE,Heute : date = CURRENT_DATE(), Gestern : date = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  1 DAY), Letztes Wochenende :  date >= (SELECT saturday FROM(SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY) as saturday)) AND date <= (SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY) as sunday), Letzte 7 Tage : date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  7 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()

query.rawSql:
SELECT 
  CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "TRUE"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN "TRUE"
  WHEN "Gestern" THEN "date = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 8 DAY)"
  WHEN "Letztes Wochenende" THEN "date >= (SELECT DATE_SUB(DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY),INTERVAL 7 DAY) as saturday) AND date <= (SELECT DATE_SUB(DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY), INTERVAL 7 DAY) as sunday)"
  WHEN "Letzte 7 Tage" THEN "date >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 14 DAY) AND date < DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)"
  WHEN "Letzte 30 Tage" THEN "date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL  60 DAY) AND date < DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL  30 DAY)"
  END

SELECT 
  CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "Heute"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN "Gestern"
  WHEN "Gestern" THEN "Gestern vor 7 Tagen"
  WHEN "Letztes Wochenende" THEN "Vorletztes Wochenende"
  WHEN "Letzte 7 Tage" THEN "Letzte 8-14 Tage"
  WHEN "Letzte 30 Tage" THEN "Letzte 31-60 Tage"
  END

SELECT 
  CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN "ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.articles_joined_today"
  ELSE "ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.articles_joined_daily"
END

SELECT distinct LRA FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
ORDER BY LRA ASC

SELECT CASE "$App"
WHEN "NDR Schleswig-Holstein" THEN "NDR SH"
WHEN "NDR Hamburg" THEN "NDR HH"
WHEN "NDR Mecklenburg-Vorpommern" THEN "NDR MV"
WHEN "NDR Elbphilharmonie Orchester" THEN "Elbphilharmonie"
WHEN "NDR Niedersachsen" THEN "NDR NDS"
WHEN "MDR Sachsen-Anhalt" THEN "MDR ST"
WHEN "Sport im Osten" THEN "MDR SPIO"
WHEN  "MDR Sachsen-Anhalt" THEN "MDR ST"
ELSE "$App"
END

SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN "$LRA" = 'MDR' THEN (
      SELECT
        distinct product_app_name
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
      WHERE
        app = "$App"
    )
    WHEN "$LRA" = 'NDR' THEN (
      SELECT
        distinct site_level2
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
      WHERE
        app = "$App"
    )
  END

SELECT distinct app FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.Profiles_App`
WHERE LRA = "$LRA"
ORDER BY app ASC

SELECT 
CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "today"
  ELSE "daily"
  END

SELECT 
CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Heute" THEN  "today"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "last_hour"
  ELSE "daily"
  END

SELECT 
CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letzte Stunde" THEN "_last_hour"
  END
